Valid-Ready Advanced FIFO
valid_ready_advanced_fifo
-------------------> clock
-------------------> resetn
-------------------> flush
-------------------> write_valid                          read_valid ------------------->
<------------------- write_ready                          read_ready <-------------------
======[WIDTH]======> write_data                            read_data ======[WIDTH]======>
<------------------- full                                      empty ------------------->
<------------------- almost_full                        almost_empty ------------------->
<------------------- half_full                            half_empty ------------------->
