<==[log₂(DEPTH)+1]== space                                     level ==[log₂(DEPTH)+1]==>
==[log₂(DEPTH)+1]==> lower_threshold_level     upper_threshold_level <==[log₂(DEPTH)+1]==
<------------------- lower_threshold_status   upper_threshold_status ------------------->